Keyword,Discovery,collects,keyword,data,from,many,different,search,engines,world,wide,and,compiles,a,range,of,search,related,statistics,KeywordDiscovery,com,offers,a,searchable,database,of,over,billion,search,queries,archived,over,a,month,period,It,enables,advertisers,and,search,engine,marketers,to,effectively,target,keyword,based,advertising,provide,advanced,keyword,research,and,analysis,of,search,trends,The,API,allows,developers,to,integrate,the,Keyword,Discovery,service,into,their,own,websites,It,uses,RESTful,calls,and,responses,are,formatted,in,XML